column2: SELECT ObjID, SpecObjID, ra, dec, u, g, r, i, z   into Mydb.Good_Calib_Data_#   from PhotoObj   WHERE (calibStatus_u & #) != #     AND (calibStatus_g & #) != #     AND (calibStatus_r & #) != #     AND (calibStatus_i & #) != #     AND (calibStatus_z & #) != #     AND psfmagerr_u < #      AND psfmagerr_g < #      AND psfmagerr_r < #      AND psfmagerr_i < #      AND psfmagerr_z < #     AND specObjID != #     AND Type = #     AND clean = #     AND htmid*# & # < (# * #)     AND SpecObjID in (       SELECT SpecObjID from SpecObjAll       WHERE segueprimary = #       AND zwarning = #     )     AND SpecObjID not in (       SELECT SpecObjID from Mydb.Good_Calib_Data2#)     ;
